    "description": "HP India Advisory Limited has an exciting opening for a Senior Software Engineer at our Chennai office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout HP India Advisory Limited:\nHP India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HP India Advisory Limited!",
